Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.33,The_Millione_Show_04:15(GCI02),Sign 0000,0000,0000,0000,,Info-Live: The Millione Show
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:05.47,Gatchaman(D)_Italics,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's Info-Live: The Millione Show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:07.80,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:11.87,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we have two guests \Nwho represent the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:15.04,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}There will be Gelsadra-kun, \Nan alien from outer space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:19.02,Alien-Gelsadra_00:14(GCI03),Sign 0015,0000,0000,0000,,Alien \NGelsadra
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:19.02,Gatchaman-Tsubasa_00:14(GCI03),Sign 0015,0000,0000,0000,,Gatchaman \NMisudachi Tsubasa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:17.87,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}and Misudachi Tsubasa-chan, \Na new Gatchaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:20.55,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Just look at those youthful smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.00,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.09,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't told of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:25.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:28.42,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:30.34,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Please show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:42.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the much talked about...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.56,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,This is everyone's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.78,0:00:48.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They seem to be calling \Nyou Bubble-sama on-line.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:51.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it'd be an alien who could \Nmake that sort of thing happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:53.51,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how is it, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:55.22,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,How is Earth to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.22,0:00:57.53,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of... disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:00:59.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:04.74,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that Earth was blue... \Nbut everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.42,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't have a blue face!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.05,0:01:09.84,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is too red!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:16.49,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's too funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.21,0:01:18.89,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,It's an alien joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:20.40,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.40,0:01:23.20,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an American joke, \Nbut an alien joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:24.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:27.92,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.56,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been so embarrassed \Nif it hadn't gone over well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,My face would've turned bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.06,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,It already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:38.34,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,You must've practiced this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:40.06,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You could tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.24,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:42.74,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.92,0:01:46.00,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:55.51,The_city_01:47(GCI03),,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(439,1)}The city \Nof teeming masses\Nis colored crimson \Nwith determination.\NA great wind will save \Nthe flame of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:49.92,Gatchaman(D)_Main,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,The city with the teeming masses
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:52.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,is colored crimson with determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,A great wind will save the flame of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.01,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,So red, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.01,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.52,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the Gatchaman base!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.57,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:40.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:42.21,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:44.74,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.49,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What was that TV appearance about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.45,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, that's... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.36,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you talking about The Millione Show?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:54.12,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't blame Tsubasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:58.45,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Millio-chan begged her, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.51,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:05.17,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I have another offer from Millio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.51,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.31,Tsubasa-phone_04:08(GCI03),Sign 0409,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan! \N Please come to The Millione Show live next week, too! \N Oh, and bring Sadra-kun with you, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:11.43,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They've both got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:12.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Director,0000,0000,0000,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Numbers, man. Numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,They're a hot item right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.68,0:04:17.94,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make them semi-regulars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a TV celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:21.99,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the Gatchaman, \Nprotectors of this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:25.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if I may,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.72,0:04:30.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think there are people who'll \Nbe encouraged if they see a hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.08,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,And we can protect them in times of need!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:40.05,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's also a hero's responsibility \Nto reassure people like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.66,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hold back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.72,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,"Leader"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.23,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hajime!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.54,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,She's a good girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:52.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What, newbie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.19,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to Gel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:57.69,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.98,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,The protection and observation \Nof extraterrestrial life forms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,are some of our duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:03.69,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,We will not cause her discomfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.57,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've brought it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:10.14,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we let Tsubasa-chan handle \NSadra-kun's observation and care?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.14,0:05:10.84,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.84,0:05:11.87,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.03,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:21.21,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I am Misudachi Tsubasa, a first-year \Nin Nagaoka City Tokiwa High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot to learn, \Nbut I'm honored to be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.47,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Gelsadra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:29.76,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You already know me, Hajime, \NOD, and Utsutsu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.80,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.75,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Utsutsu-senpai, nice to meet you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.63,Gatchaman(D)_Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gloomy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:37.77,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Those three, you're meeting \Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,First, that's Hibiki Jou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:42.00,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tachibana Sugane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.67,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Tsubasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:47.36,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:51.41,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,And last but not least, this is Ninomiya \NRui, who joined right before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.43,0:05:54.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,You're much girlier than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.12,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.23,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.36,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to introduce him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:02.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the upstart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.08,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,I wants a story where the \Ninnocent country bumpkin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:06.42,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,gets corrupted by the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.98,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where's that voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.18,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's Katze-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.96,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sadra,0000,0000,0000,,Berg-Katze?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.03,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know him, Gel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.82,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sadra,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:17.12,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sadra,0000,0000,0000,,He's very famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.20,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a simpleton, Geruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.25,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,"This is everyone's feelings"—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.95,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,You're dreamin—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:28.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Katze-san's in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.04,0:06:30.25,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:31.82,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.35,0:06:34.49,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,but pleased to meet you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:38.57,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we use this opportunity \Nto throw a welcome party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:41.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I guess Tsubasa-chan can't drink yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.63,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Sugane, now's not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.26,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Jou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:50.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to ignore JJ's prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:54.79,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.32,0:06:59.50,The_city_06:53(GCI03),Sign 0656,0000,0000,0000,,The city \Nof teeming masses\Nis colored crimson \Nwith determination.\NA great wind will save \Nthe flame of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:55.66,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:59.52,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,JJ's words guide our actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.15,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,The "flame of life"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.35,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,A "great wind"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.99,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,JJ is way too vague, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:08.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson refers to red, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:10.49,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,I have some ideas about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.62,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,If we're talking red...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:13.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,we're talking about CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.53,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,VAPE, the organization \Ncontrolling the red CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:19.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,During their previous attack on Nagaoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:22.25,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,a man identifying himself as their \Nleader showed up in front of Rui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.25,0:07:25.11,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he said to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.59,0:07:28.40,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,that they were violent pacifists...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Violent... pacifists...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.55,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time to be \Nfinding them interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.66,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Why would pacifists \Ndo such horrible things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.19,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,To wipe CROWDS out from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:44.54,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,They're intentionally \Ncausing havoc with CROWDS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.54,0:07:47.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,so that people would realize \Nthe threat CROWDS pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:52.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But isn't it just the red \NCROWDS who are dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Not necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:58.14,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,There were some reports of pranks \Nand crimes committed by blue CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.77,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,X just took care of them before \Nthings got too out of hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.71,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,so they never received \Nmuch attention. That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.64,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:09.27,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, humanity wasn't \Nready for the CROWDS ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:10.93,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.84,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, there are people \Nwho use CROWDS for crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:19.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But nothing goes well on the first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:22.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We should move forward, \Neven if we have to fail several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to believe in evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,but what if society collapses \Nbefore that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we have \Nall the time in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:34.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think updating the world \Nwill take that much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:38.49,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The VAPE leader is a self-driven \Nman in the extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:41.43,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He has taken a wrong turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:43.38,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's very principled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.17,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If there were more people \Nlike him who could direct
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.45,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,their energy on the right path...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.96,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,If there were, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.96,0:08:49.42,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You're being idealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:52.17,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of having \Na world without ideals?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.59,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.93,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:01.50,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to become a hero \Nwho can protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try my best to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.35,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.15,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,The newbie is far more realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:16.39,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Room 103 will be for the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.40,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.44,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You must be tired from the long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:25.16,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Your beds are ready, \Nso you should go to sleep early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Rui-senpai, you're really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.80,0:09:30.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:35.08,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I was just thinking that you and Jou-san
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,must have a similar sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.79,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Katze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Katze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.34,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:47.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,If the VAPE leader can control CROWDS,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,that means he's had his NOTE extracted,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:51.41,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,just like Rui-kun's was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:52.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Silence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:56.93,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,The only one I know who can \Ndo that is you, Katze-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:58.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,but is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Katze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.45,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Katze-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:02.38,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:04.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was enjoying my relaxation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.61,0:10:05.65,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, fine, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.65,0:10:08.00,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who extracted Rizumin's NOTE,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.38,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,but so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a problem with that, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:14.76,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person is he? \NThe VAPE leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:17.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you could say he's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.11,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Totes serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:23.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,But those types are the worst \Nwhen they snap, ya know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.65,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's begin, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:41.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:46.66,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,It's VAPE!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:58.20,Live_Broadcast_10:55(GCI03),Sign 1057,0000,0000,0000,,[Live Broadcast] Crisis in Shibuya! Red CROWDS Rioting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.22,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what this is about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.47,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:00.47,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.48,Urgent_News_11:07(GCI03),Sign 1108,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent News: Panic in Shibuya! \N Red CROWDS Appear en Masse--City Turns Scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.48,Shibuya;_Tokyo_11:07(GCI03),Sign 1108,0000,0000,0000,,Shibuya, Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:09.89,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seeing this, viewers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.23,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The entire city of Shibuya is scarlet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:16.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.67,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are they hostages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Several citizens appear to be \Nrestrained by the red CROWDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look! Blue CROWDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.36,Don't_underestimate_us_11:25(GCI03),Sign 1127,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us, \Nred CROWDS!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:34.79,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sign 1127,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.65,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sign 1127,0000,0000,0000,,They're powerless!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.80,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Their organization is \Nalmost organized military.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.31,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,The blue CROWDS have no organization. \NThey don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,We Gatchaman are the ones \Nwho protect the planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:58.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gs,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.34,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:08.04,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:11.41,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gs,0000,0000,0000,,Gatcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.54,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Gatchaman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.46,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Gatchaman have come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.46,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sign 1221,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:23.38,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:28.26,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't even \Ntransform at will yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.18,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you just hold everyone back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.50,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:38.73,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Sonic Demon Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.48,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Feather!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:53.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,Fight until this life of mine \Nis extinguished, my shards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.22,Gatchaman(D)_Main,UShards,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:59.38,Gatchaman(D)_Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Bite and Build!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:02.92,Gatchaman(D)_Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,The Right Arm of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.76,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Petites Ciseaux!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:14.69,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Blanc et Noir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Digitize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.08,Caller_ID_blocked_13:28(GCI03),Sign 1330,0000,0000,0000,,Caller ID Blocked
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.40,0:13:34.84,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ninomiya Rui-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.25,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This is Suzuki Rizumu, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:39.75,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Ninomiya Rui, hand over your NOTE.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:41.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Then people will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:53.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, we have kept human \Ncasualties to a minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:55.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,That will end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.74,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to abandon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.20,0:14:02.14,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to avert your gaze \Nagain from the lives that were lost
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:05.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,and continue to only preach \Nthe utility of CROWDS?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.60,0:14:09.66,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you did for \Nthe Tachikawa Incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you had noticed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.40,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,that in the shadows of your victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.40,0:14:19.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,there were those who fell victim to CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.74,0:14:23.15,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your isolation,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:27.17,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Ninomiya Rui-kun, you foolish idealist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.18,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Hajime-chan, I'm leaving this to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:33.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:48.41,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's Ninomiya Rui-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.41,0:14:50.59,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that before him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:52.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Is he one of the VAPE members?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.20,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you reject CROWDS so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.91,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Monkeys don't deserve such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.84,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,In time, CROWDS will just \Nbecome a means for violence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.46,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,for monkeys are easily \Nswayed by public opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.06,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:08.13,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,People can change!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Two to six to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.39,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Only a handful can change.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,You know that in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:18.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:21.82,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I believe each and every \None of us can evolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.82,0:15:23.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,To update the world, we need—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.85,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop with the idealism.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:29.98,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want to lose CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.35,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you look like a spoiled child
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:40.00,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,who doesn't want his \NCROWDS toy taken from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.59,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Out, Bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.95,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:51.68,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ninomiya Rui-san has transformed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.80,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to pull, Rui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.83,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You may be right in that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:59.39,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fixated on the idea of CROWDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.23,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding fast to my hope. \NI want to believe in everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:09.57,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.50,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,if I also believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.45,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.50,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.64,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,that you are a man who \Nis driven by the right principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.44,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,Ninomiya Rui-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.51,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,you're so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:03.33,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,so... foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:05.75,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.85,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Rui-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.91,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Ninomiya Rui-san just collapsed, \Nwith blood coming out of his mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:11.75,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:13.65,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Someone call the ambulance! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:15.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:19.29,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,What are the other Gatchaman doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.73,Gatchaman(D)_Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,Rui-kun, we're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.64,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:23.53,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.86,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Rui-san's getting up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:28.81,Gatchaman(D)_Main,M,0000,0000,0000,,Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.81,0:17:31.53,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This... is my fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:33.77,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.16,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe in him until the very end...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:38.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:40.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Now isn't a time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.32,0:17:42.65,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Jou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.65,0:17:43.70,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:46.02,Gatchaman(D)_Main,J,0000,0000,0000,,Sugane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:53.10,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be what kills you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.30,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Ri,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be your foolish ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:03.60,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Rui-rui blood-fest, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.60,0:18:05.73,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rizumin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:08.11,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Sugane,0000,0000,0000,,So, so yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:10.52,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Katze-san, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.61,More_Urgent_News_18:10(GCI03),Sign 1812,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent News: Mr. Ninomiya Rui Bleeding! \N Gatchaman vs. VAPE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,How could he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.42,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,He'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.22,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,No, Tsubasa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:22.63,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.11,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.68,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,This needs to stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.19,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.72,Gatchaman(D)_Announcer,M,0000,0000,0000,,Someone do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:33.96,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.91,0:18:36.83,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:40.01,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What good are we if we don't go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:43.39,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Gatchaman are \Nheroes who protect everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.77,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.07,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,It's our mission to protect people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.24,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,But Tsubasa-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.99,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,people have principles \Nthat can't be sacrificed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.56,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,even if it means losing their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.10,0:18:58.57,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Rui-kun's fighting that fight right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.77,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:03.74,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.18,Gatchaman(D)_Main,OD,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.17,0:19:10.37,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:35.02,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.69,Bubbles_19:35(GCI03),Sign 1936,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this \NPlease help him \NSomeone do something  \NScrew you, VAPE \NRui-kun's gonna die! \NThis is too horrible  \NWhat's the gov't doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.69,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.40,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:43.12,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:44.87,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Please get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.83,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.97,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.90,Gatchaman(D)_Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubasa-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.83,0:20:15.18,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't help people in need,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:20.96,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,how can we call ourselves heroes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.64,Gatchaman(D)_Main,T,0000,0000,0000,,Hundred Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:46.28,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:20:57.73,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what everyone wants...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.89,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,we'll become heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.99,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.55,Gatchaman(D)_Main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:40.59,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,Take flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.39,0:21:44.61,Gatchaman(D)_Main,Gel,0000,0000,0000,,wings of hope!
